{"tid":1754703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（光復香港藍圖）區選大勝後，香港人最應該擔心嘅係要點打呢場順境波","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:39:32.000Z","uid":219269,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ac731f8411f7c7e27108d3b235863ab8c72afdf0","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"香港人必須承認我地唔係好識把握優勢，滾雪球咁樣贏落去<br />\n因為一直以嚟我地都係打逆境波為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/frown_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講咁多廢話，以下事項分緩急輕重列出：<br />\n<br />\n1. 營救理大手足（打緊篇文嘅一刻，范國威宣布派5個人交涉）<br />\n最緊要記住18號嘅教訓，要be smart<br />\n諗清楚行動嘅手段同目的相唔相符<br />\n例如若果大量群眾嘅人潮做唔到直接營救<br />\n可以響東西九龍聲東擊西，調虎離山<br />\n<br />\n2. 申請選舉呈請，為有問題選區重選或重新點票<br />\n既然係有問題，有程序不當嘅選舉，我地都唔好放過<br />\n有機會將對方打壓到盡，絕對唔好放過，打到佢地完全一敗糊塗<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢個一定會係滾起雪球嘅第一步！！！</span><br />\n詳細資訊：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754328</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 立即向法庭申請禁制令，禁止銷毀區議會財政文件<br />\n再進一步乘勝追擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/http://na.cx/i/PMg7trT.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754197</a><br />\n<br />\n完成以上較迫切嘅行動先<br />\n4. 開始善用區議會嘅資源，協助光復香港<br />\n呢樣需要從長計議，參考一下保皇黨提供利益嘅方法話唔定可以瓦解鐵票<br />\n<blockquote>區議員每月酬金為33,950元，或每年407,400元；完成任期後，將會獲得酬金總數15%的任滿酬金(244,200)。<br />\n<br />\n實報實銷開支<br />\n每年537,792元營運開支（包括員工薪酬），支付執行區議會職務所需開支；<br />\n每屆任期120,000元，用以支付開設議員辦事處所需開支；<br />\n每年34,320元，用以支付區議員醫療保險或醫療開支的費用；<br />\n每屆任期不多於10,000元，用以區議員的外訪開支。<br />\n<br />\n非實報實銷開支<br />\n每年92,280元，支付交通及小額雜項開支津貼。<br />\n<br />\n建制派僅得59席，佔區議會13%，較上屆失244席<br />\n244個議席<br />\n4年加埋起碼11億元</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753984</a><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住權力要用到盡，唔好再好似以前咁戇鳩鳩，記住今次係一場鬥爭</span><br />\n泛民如果識玩.區議會可以權力好大<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753668</a>"},{"pid":"b891bc2f1104542095089e228d26893c47e5b844","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13e2c1324ab267fd781dbe9b15856e9c8ad9d0c","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5bfc967839af438d6bc2e163034dcf06a9b5d","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/frown_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e21c9fe233e64b7ecbae41e1763a2f25853a0ec","tid":1754703,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"cfd1a9a0df8ce43ce0bf88018ad74554709a9ea7","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85725b7ba4a2b9242572231a42d834d6637980df","tid":1754703,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4ae79fbf3be7a0526034bf393f0eae80f338fba","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"今次有冇咩隱藏嘅emoji"},{"pid":"2495125929ea16ffd758bf3c66d056e7ce63f747","tid":1754703,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a920b8be3855ed3c56f4e340df9a441294d35be","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">第二點係一敗<del>糊</del>塗地</span>"},{"pid":"15e1a8a1ac10a22da75cd5ae57731ba341608682","tid":1754703,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"唔好推啦"},{"pid":"0097fb09177d64d3dfe27a6a781edd96aee469fa","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15e1a8a1ac10a22da75cd5ae57731ba341608682","tid":1754703,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"唔好推啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/frown_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57587dbca9e1afc8889496fa84c044479dda51b5","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5c1f9d1f18677941f4de87a1b7c78f81868e24","tid":1754703,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"雖然區選拎左389席<br />\n但咁嘅選舉制度下仲比建制狗拎到59席<br />\n只可以叫做小勝<br />\n大家開心完之後抗爭運動都要繼續落去<br />\nPOLY仲有一大班手足畀狗圍緊<br />\n仲有好多手足畀狗拉左畀人告緊<br />\n佢地等緊我地光復香港救佢地出黎<br />\n如果我地區選完就退<br />\n點對得住死左嘅手足<br />\n點對得住為我地擋子彈嘅手足<br />\n點對得住畀狗拉左嘅手足<br />\n所以18區要繼續開花<br />\n黎明行動要日日搞<br />\n組織全港大三罷<br />\n直到光復香港為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db9234351b13e4f9e35a8b186bf138bd5b6ec90","tid":1754703,"uid":109706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"我地贏係因為政府不停犯錯,千萬要小心唔好自滿,鬆懈.要團結一致.<br />\n要為被捕既人,同死傷者取回公道.<br />\n<br />\n光複香港.時代革命"},{"pid":"df1c3ff172917d6e448ecdb50c8762a85d4acd4d","tid":1754703,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"未打過順境波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bdaf435b95ce5b2f49d575bc7b8c85f1b7351c","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dfdde3a05115eb648b02661a2ab09e070ee3f7b","tid":1754703,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"仲未係順景波，不要開心太早"},{"pid":"ddfcabe4430caf1c020f19c5910f350697e7b9df","tid":1754703,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfdde3a05115eb648b02661a2ab09e070ee3f7b","tid":1754703,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"仲未係順景波，不要開心太早"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"只係戰事剛剛開始"},{"pid":"ef30cfb7d1d931ea9ea51f6ef3f6c08a644faf09","tid":1754703,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"761b1b99ebe00f81aeb787dc6f90aac4d78d52ed","tid":1754703,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"贊成"},{"pid":"58da83dba9a51b729612f35d6592524efc21e915","tid":1754703,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"贊成要商討藍圖"},{"pid":"37436ea86ae6f54627aef74195f29c7d6d1e5d98","tid":1754703,"uid":51551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"謹記無大台，唔好俾區議會主導後續運動"},{"pid":"88bd920d4c16ccf14a67745766c05112f8ee103a","tid":1754703,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192931550f731b0a94fe41cd78fea3d9c21577b0","tid":1754703,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfdde3a05115eb648b02661a2ab09e070ee3f7b","tid":1754703,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"仲未係順景波，不要開心太早"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"就係因為要打唔擅長嘅順境波<br />\n所以唔會開心住"}]}